Outside, the fully enclosed backyard provides a safe space for children to play and includes two garden sheds for extra storage and undercover parking.

This home offers both comfort and convenience in a prime location!

Outdoors, you'll find an undercover area that's perfect for barbecues or simply enjoying the fresh air. The low maintenance backyard is fully enclosed. There is also a shed available for use in the backyard and the front yard has established garden beds.

Overall, this rental house is the perfect place to call home, with its stunning features, modern amenities, and hard to beat location. It is the perfect combination of modern fittings which have been done in a way which still respects the stunning original feature of the property.
